title: EU proposes to limit Ukraine imports, ease green rules as farmers take protest to Brussels
description: With farmers venting their anger across Europe, the European Union said Wednesday it would create "safeguards" to stop cheap Ukrainian imports from flooding the market and ease highly contested rules on leaving land unused. FRANCE 24's Brussels correspondent …
